  "prompt": "International awards of Shahrukh Khan?",
  "response": "Shah Rukh Khan, often referred to as the \"King of Bollywood,\" has garnered international recognition for his contributions to cinema and global culture. Here are some of the notable international awards and honors he has received up to October 2023:\n\n1. **Legion of Honour (Chevalier de la L\u00e9gion d'Honneur) \u2013 France (2023)**\n   - **Description:** France's highest civilian award, the Legion of Honour, was bestowed upon Shah Rukh Khan in 2023. This prestigious recognition acknowledged his significant contributions to the arts and his role in promoting French-Indian cultural relations through cinema.\n\n2. **Order of Arts and Letters (Ordre des Arts et des Lettres) \u2013 France (2007)**\n   - **Description:** Shah Rukh Khan was honored as a Chevalier (Knight) of the Order of Arts and Letters by the French government. This award recognizes individuals who have made significant contributions to the arts and literature, or the propagation of these fields.\n\n3. **UNESCO Pyramide con Marni Award (2006)**\n   - **Description:** Awarded by UNESCO in collaboration with the Pyramide con Marni Foundation, this honor recognized Khan for his efforts in promoting cross-cultural dialogue and understanding through his work in cinema.\n\n4. **Honorary Doctorate from the University of Edinburgh (2011)**\n   - **Description:** In recognition of his contributions to the global entertainment industry and his influence in promoting Indian cinema worldwide, Shah Rukh Khan received an honorary doctorate from the University of Edinburgh.\n\n5. **Global Indian Film Personality Awards**\n   - **Description:** While not a single award, Shah Rukh Khan has been a prominent figure at various international platforms celebrating Indian cinema, including receiving lifetime achievement honors and acknowledgments at events like the Global Indian Film Personality Awards.\n\n6. **World Economic Forum \u2013 Young Global Leaders (2005)**\n   - **Description:** Although not solely an entertainment award, Khan's inclusion as a Young Global Leader highlighted his influence beyond cinema, acknowledging his role in shaping global cultural narratives.\n\n7. **Honorary Ambassador Roles**\n   - **Description:** Shah Rukh Khan has served as an honorary ambassador for various international initiatives, including those related to health, education, and cultural diplomacy, further cementing his global stature.\n\n8. **Other International Recognitions**\n   - **Description:** Over the years, Khan has received numerous accolades from international film festivals, cultural organizations, and media outlets, celebrating his versatility as an actor and his impact on global audiences.\n\n**Note:** While Shah Rukh Khan has received numerous international honors, the majority of his awards and recognitions come from Indian institutions and film industry bodies. His global awards are a testament to his widespread appeal and influence beyond the Indian subcontinent.",
